  "title": "MineFortress",
  "description": "the mod that will turn your Minecraft into real-time strategy like Rimworld or DwarfFortress. Take the role of a village leader, gather resources, build houses, hire professionals to grow and expand your village and even conquer your neighbors!",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n\t<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8GzVzNN.png\" alt=\"minefortress banner\"/>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n\t<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/minefortress\" alt=\"support me on patreon\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/PATREON-SUPPORT_ME-f96854?style=for-the-badge&logo=patreon&logoColor=f96854&labelColor=052d49&color=f96854\"/>\n\t</a>\n\t<a href=\"https://discord.gg/6rt7VJxPcq\" alt=\"join our discord server\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/906943962659561515?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&label=discord&color=5865F2\"/>\n\t</a>\n\t<a href=\"https://www.minefortress.net/?utm_source=modrinth\" alt=\"our website\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/website-minefortress-CC9966?style=for-the-badge\"/>\n\t</a>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n\t<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Nts5I2Y.jpg\" />\n\t<h3>📚 ABOUT THE MOD 📚</h3>\n</p>\nThe mod turns your Minecraft into RTS. Take the role of a village leader, gather resources, build houses, hire professionals to grow    and expand your village and even conquer your neighbors! Forget about the first-person view and control everything with your mouse pointer like in classic RTS games. \n\nFeatures:\n - Truly RTS-like view. Control everything with your mouse pointer! \n - Resources system. Your pawns will gather resources, and you can spend them to hire more professionals, or to build some houses. \n - Blueprints system. Build your custom buildings and add them to your very own village. \n - Combat system! Hire warriors and go fight with your neighbors! \n - Hunger and mood system. Your pawns have their health stats and in the future will have their mood and    character. \n - Multiplayer support starting with 1.8.3 beta version\n<p align=\"center\">\n\t<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Nts5I2Y.jpg\" />\n\t<h3>🎥 TAKE A LOOK! 🎥</h3>\n</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/fkHgeUocvVk\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/8SJ9x64BLbg\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/MgYR0pJP-1I\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p align=\"center\">\n\t<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Nts5I2Y.jpg\" />\n\t<h3>📚 INSTALLATION 📚</h3>\n</p>\n<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/modloader-Fabric-1976d2?style=for-the-badge&logo=data:image/png;base64,\"/> \n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><img width=\"200px\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" /></a>\n\nInstallation should be pretty straightforward. \n1. Install Fabric Launcher\n2. Add Latest Fabric API compatible the mod if it's not installed automatically \n3. Add the mod\n<p align=\"center\">\n\t<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Nts5I2Y.jpg\" />\n\t<h3>🎮 GETTING STARTED 🎮</h3>\n</p>\nThe mod adds new Gamemode to the game named \"Fortress\"\n\n**Choose gamemode \"Fortress\" in the World Creation Menu or use \"/gamemode fortress\" command while playing** and you will be switched to Fortress gamemode.\n\nYour main control in the game is you mouse pointer. After starting the world right click to place campfire.\n\nBasic controls:\n- left click once - start selecting a task to \"dig\"/remove something\n- left click while selecting - confirm \"dig\" task\n- right click while holding any block in hand - start selecting  a task to build something\n- right click while selecting - confirm \"build\" task\n- hold sprint button (ctrl by default) and move your mouse - look around\n<p align=\"center\">\n\t<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Nts5I2Y.jpg\" />\n\t<h3>🤑 SUPPORT THE PROJECT 🤑</h3>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/minefortress\">\n<img width=\"300px\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/eqJC3SgJf3RQMAFl2ynpOplm2sJcCa837NvQeOKSpBbs5PVWs9N7lCQT3zFaWx8NsM0=w2400\" />\n</a>\n</p>\n",
